sources.authors: Umpress, S. T., Murphy, S. P., Franke, A. A., Custer, L. J., and Blitz, C. L.

footnotes.desc: Samples were obtained from 12 retail stores using a probability-based sampling plan.  Some fish had been treated during processing to retain moisture on thawing.  Untreated fish = 56 mg sodium/100g.
